<h2>Reminder: You have access to a LIVE video stream with <%= @band.name %></h2>

<p>The next stream, <%= @stream.title+", will be starting on"%> <strong><%= stream_starts_at.strftime("%A %B %d, %Y at %I:%M:%p ET.") %> Note the time given is in the Eastern Timezone.</strong></p>

<p>Please login with the email address <strong><%= @user.email %></strong> to watch the stream during the scheduled time.</p>

<p>If you are unable to view the stream live, you can view a recording of the stream 24 hours after the scheduled start time.</p>
  
<br/>

<p>
  You have permissions to view all streams within the following series:
  <br/>
  <%= @lss.title %>
</p>

<p>
  To view times for other streams in this series, please visit the 
  <% if @band.access_schedule_url.nil? || @band.access_schedule_url == '' %>
    band's website.
  <% else %>
    <%= link_to 'Stream Viewer', @band.access_schedule_url %>
  <% end %>
  <br/>
  and login with your credentials.
</p>

<p>
  Thanks,
  <br/>
  The MyBandStock Team
  <br/> 
  <br/>
</p>

<p>
  <% if @user.nil? %>
    If you do not wish to receive emails in the future, please go to your MyBandStock.com user account settings and edit your email notification options.  
  <% else %>
      If you do not wish to receive emails in the future, please go to your <%= link_to 'User Profile', @mbslink+'/users/'+@user.id.to_s+'/edit' %> and edit your email notification settings.  
  <% end %>
  If you forgot your MyBandStock password, you can <%= link_to 'reset your password', @mbslink+'/me/forgot_password' %>.  For questions, please contact <%= @support_email %>.
</p>
